headline: Comcast, Classiq and AMD Demonstrate Quantum Algorithm for More Resilient and Reliable Internet
summary: PHILADELPHIA & TEL AVIV, Israel, February 17, 2026--Classiq, the leading quantum computing software company, Comcast and AMD today announced the completion of a groundbreaking trial aimed at improving Internet delivery by leveraging quantum algorithms to supercharge network routing resilience.
